Lesson 7 Are you a teacher?

Listen to the tape then answer this question.

What is Robert job?

I am a new student.

My names Robert.

Nice too meet you.

My names Sophie.

Are you French?

Yes, I am.

Are you French, too?

No, I am not.

What nationality are you ?

Im Italian.

Are you a teacher?

No, Im not.

Whats you job?

Im a keyboard operator.

Whats you job?

Im an engineer.
